Resource Profile: FI Base Information Custodian (Individual Provider)

Official URL: https://hl7.fi/fhir/finnish-base-profiles/StructureDefinition/fi-base-information-custodian-individual Version: 1.0.0-rc21
Draft as of 2023-10-23 Computable Name: FiBaseInformationCustodianIndividual

This is the Finnish base profile for the Provenance resource, used to communicate an individual practitioner as the custodian of information (rekisterinpitäjä).

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Provenance/custodian-individual

Description of Profiles, Differentials, Snapshots and how the different presentations work.
